Trinity::

She cheered as she went with him.  She waved her tiny paws at 
Archangle as she went with Aerotaur. "BYE Archangle, I'm going to 
find my mom and dad! I'll be back for you. Bye!"  She giggled 
slightly, she was going to see her parents again and she couldn't 
contain her excitement.
